<p>The game has always been known as football in Australia whilst soccer, being the 4th most popular sport in the country after Australian Rules, then League, then rugby.</p>
<p>Trying to call the game &#8220;football&#8221; is simply confusing. Probably explains the dismal state of soccer.</p>
